title: Elemental Awareness: From Kickflip to Campfire
description:
Elemental Awareness is the foundation associated with Element Skateboards, and aims to connect youth to nature through skateboarding. Instructor Mat Luciani gives an explanation of our summer survival course offered at Element Skate Camp. For more information visit Elementalawareness.org

Filmed by:
Tom Mull
Mitch Buangsuwon

Edited by:
Mitch Buangsuwon
